{"tid":2393282,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"我沒勇氣再Strong Hold GME","createTime":"2021-02-03T10:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T11:10:42.000Z","uid":286928,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b371defe7ca4b32017147e8b944c3837eb2a5b93","tid":2393282,"uid":286928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"好好Stop loss 應要淡忘<br />\n我找到ARKK<br />\n回望在年初  我有身家上百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重臨舊情景  我會一早止賺毫不客氣<br />\n<br />\n然而自己現在沒任何權利  再抱怨一句<br />\n我再沒勇氣 再望盤前<br />\n沒有勇氣  再Strong Hold GME<br />\n大户早已經高位散場  再Strong Hold並無意義<br />\n<br />\n緣分到此  含淚止蝕是年紀小的心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今天已全忘記 個倉已回彈不需記掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：蝕左三位數USD 指數V彈個倉都未升返高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c796887925d5392e27df7fcc52b31207c32ca49","tid":2393282,"uid":300690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"邊間教會"},{"pid":"e34be928a925e40527f6f5b428d3ba4360934773","tid":2393282,"uid":15033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLdTMPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLdTMPS.jpg&h=6822a368&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40c64897abd06fc94c3b5633a1da083bdd1cd8d3","tid":2393282,"uid":120210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c796887925d5392e27df7fcc52b31207c32ca49","tid":2393282,"uid":300690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"邊間教會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"樓主直頭係教宗"}]}